that would allow the PyPA to create some kind of snapshot

00:28:01.740 --> 00:28:04.540
that says, even if those mirrors went away,

00:28:04.940 --> 00:28:07.960
this is the reality of things, right?

00:28:08.680 --> 00:28:10.760
I mean, it's one thing to say, well,

