And you're building those into your Docker, right?

00:29:05.500 --> 00:29:06.400
So it's not just availability.

00:29:08.200 --> 00:29:09.940
It's not just availability and fallback.

00:29:10.300 --> 00:29:11.140
It is consistency.

00:29:11.620 --> 00:29:14.260
So that when you push an update, it forces an update, right?

00:29:14.480 --> 00:29:14.740
Right.

